{
  "stem": "19969.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But it took us two or three days-- that's a large city.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "It took us two or three days to clear it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I had very few casualties, probably not more than 20 in my battalion in Nuremberg, very light casualties.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "But we captured several thousand Germans there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And then right outside of Nuremberg, then, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] as we were-- the whole army was regrouping to make-- our objective was the city of Munich.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "That was the Seventh Army-- one of the Seventh Army objectives.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Because that was the capital city of Bavaria.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And we were-- Nuremberg, we were operating in Bavaria.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And that was considered to be the transportation, supply, and command hub of Bavaria.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And therefore, it was a critical objective as far as the Seventh Army.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Our division was part of the Seventh United States Army.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "On our left was the Third United States Army.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And our mission was to get to Munich as rapidly as possible before the Germans had a chance to consolidate defensive positions.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Right outside of a-- as we left Nuremberg, the day-- the day before we departed, I was designated as a task force commander and given a battalion of tanks to-- with my infantry battalion, plus two artillery batteries and some engineers.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And the tanks was-- a battalion of tanks, that's about 54 tanks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And my orders were to proceed as rapidly as possible towards Munich, to bypass any opposition if I got too much opposition, and that following forces would clean it up.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "But I was to barrel into Munich as rapidly as I could.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Well, of course, with these tanks, I had all the tanks that the division had.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "I only had-- they only had one battalion.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "So I divided it up into two prongs.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
